ISG researchers won the  Mark Weiser Best Paper Award at IEEE PERCOM 2022


       ISG researchers won the Mark Weiser Best Paper Award at IEEE PERCOM 2022 For their paper entitled SmartSPEC: Customizable Smart Space Datasets via Event-Driven Simulations. This work, co-authored by Andrew Chio, Daokun Jiang, Peeyush Gupta, Georgios Vouloukakis, Roberto Yus, Sharad Mehrotra, and Nalini Venkatasubramanian,  developed a novel event-based simulator for generating synthetic smart space data. The simulator was inspired by…         Continue Reading




